# Local TTS virtualenv for the tts-voiceover engine (Kokoro + torch, multi-GB).
# Created on the host where /short runs; never committed. See
# .claude/skills/tts-voiceover/SKILL.md for how to recreate it.
.venv-tts/
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Rendered/mastered video outputs + thumbnails — regenerable by scripts/render-run.mjs.
# The spec package (00..08 .md, vo.wav, vo-timing.json, assets/) is the source of truth.
# Covers final/-best/-vN/-v3-N takes and any other mp4 under a run folder.
output/**/*.mp4
output/**/*.png
render/out/
